https://webdesign.tutsplus.com/tutorials/watch-and-compile-sass-in-five-quick-steps--cms-28275


STEPS:

npm init

npm install node-sass

scripts:
    scss:node-sass --watch scss -o css

will look in scss directory and put it in css directory: (YOU HAVE TO MAKE BOTH BEFORE THIS SCRIPT WILL RUN (files too))
npm run scss
